  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1354511">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1354511/" class="title-link">乡谣何在</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1354511"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/bigandbig/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1062144-85.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bigandbig/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">月兑月兑胖了</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-04-16"
      class="main-meta">2008-04-16 15:30:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1354511_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                       《遥远的乡愁》为人诟病最主要的罪状是，这里有历史却没有音乐。对这样的评价我只能说，这是一本关于台湾民谣史的书，想听音乐的人应该去买林生祥演出的入场券。音乐在现场；想通过阅读来“理解”音乐，等于爬到梧桐树上找鲤鱼。我们似已习惯了以“理解”的方式来应对生活...

