  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1277482/" class="title-link">关于台湾“民歌运动”中的“民歌”（修订版）</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1277482"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/matt-viola/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1074433-30.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/matt-viola/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">玛特</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-01-09"
      class="main-meta">2008-01-09 11:36:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1277482_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  台湾的“民歌运动”是台湾社会转型初期（台湾退出联合国、台美断交到解严前后）由知识界发起的音乐运动，它有明显的政治、社会诉求。从整体而言，“民歌运动”中出现的作品，不是真本土的，因此是无根的，不能代表台湾的乡土音乐传统。它本质上仍深具意识形态色彩，只是归属的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1277482/#comments">(8回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">19有用 / 8没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
