  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/127017430/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u127017430-3.jpg" class="pil" alt="△" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/127017430/">△</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          昨天          想读      </div>

      <br/>


    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/156960015/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u156960015-1.jpg" class="pil" alt="董大宝" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/156960015/">董大宝</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          6月15日          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar20" title="较差"></span>
      <br/>


          <span class="">买不到《谁在那边唱歌》，只买了这本，有点失望。前者看过一些前段和再版序，感觉是张钊维以做学问的态度来解读台湾民歌运动乃至流行文化，而后者功力只到娱乐版记者的层次，只有资料罗列，而且感情也过于泛滥。不过这就是目前现状，不是所有的书都买得到。</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/entrance0307/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46107351-13.jpg" class="pil" alt="foi" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/entrance0307/">foi</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          6月13日          想读      </div>

      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:台湾 音乐</span><br />

    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>


